{"tid":1864654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係咪忘記左「臨時政府」？","createTime":"2020-02-05T17:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T06:46:47.000Z","uid":39703,"like":89,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"67c614ed4a2c0c2573f199834211875cada32a12","tid":1864654,"uid":39703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:14:18.000Z","msg":"由六月到而家<br />\n我地都好清楚林鄭係唔會答應香港人既訴求<br />\n撤回送中條例用左四個月先撤到<br />\n其餘四個訴求一慨不理<br />\n繼續我行我素<br />\n當時已經話唔排除會成立臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n而家 疫症爆發<br />\n大家都見到呢個港共政府有幾無能<br />\n不封關<br />\n不分配口罩俾市民<br />\n大話連篇<br />\n置香港醫護同大眾市民於疫症之中<br />\n甚至 曾經站在道德高地既醫護都罷工<br />\n但呢個垃圾政府繼續無視訴求<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候不分藍黃都係到屌緊呢個政府無能<br />\n當初講既成立臨時政府去左邊？ <br />\n而家就係最需要臨時政府<br />\n推翻港共政府 <br />\n真正守護香港 保護香港人<br />\n<br />\n#康復香港時代抗疫<br />\n#光復香港時代革命<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可"},{"pid":"dee37b2ecc5ef38d7e419a71c4059467e30abd4e","tid":1864654,"uid":39703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OknXSs7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOknXSs7.jpg&h=bcb2896a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kELB71s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkELB71s.jpg&h=1c0ea358&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b77b5abd263d532a96a7792115e5d92e8dd44e9","tid":1864654,"uid":39703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:16:48.000Z","msg":"政府並無提供足夠防護裝備俾醫護<br />\n係嚴重危害醫護生命安全！！！"},{"pid":"b638513736402be261cd88614c91a45b8c3bb28d","tid":1864654,"uid":18147,"like":35,"dislike":12,"score":23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:17:26.000Z","msg":"認受性？<br />\n<br />\n邊個出錢？<br />\n<br />\n對家有警察， 你有咩？<br />\n<br />\n國際認唔諗同你？<br />\n<br />\nConclusion, 早d 訓"},{"pid":"cd1c6ba4c2accc8e067e91701124b82ee0b36a81","tid":1864654,"uid":39703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:17:33.000Z","msg":"From ha secret<br />\n<br />\n#9736<br />\n&quot;內部消息<br />\n1. alochol swab 全HA 唔夠一個月貨，並且未揾到supplier會送貨<br />\n2. 暫時我部門得返嘅外科手術口罩存量只餘十數日，N95 不足一週，要等上頭配給<br />\n3. 重點推介： 暫時醫2019-nCov嘅藥物三寶：kaletra,  ribavirin,  interferon beta-1b,  第三樣已經得返極少量，最快四月*可能*先有貨；第一樣嘅水劑專for tube咗要經胃喉服藥嘅重症病人，同樣得返極少量<br />\n4. 全球都搶緊藥<br />\n<br />\n結論1：可能今個月內，香港已經會發生廣泛性「醫護無保護，病人無藥醫｣嘅災難。<br />\n<br />\n結論2：封關呀仆街！！！！！&quot;"},{"pid":"8a0b152efc66949906a99b07a694aa9a204ca46c","tid":1864654,"uid":90971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:18:20.000Z","msg":"呢幾日都諗緊呢樣嘢"},{"pid":"dd39b4be9a4f6cf4432811daa06d2a6a388412d5","tid":1864654,"uid":34422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edcac16fb18cea54958a682aa9b4e73c4e478657","tid":1864654,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:18:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8611f4fd4ff17e80beafde856d9afd4d0b517d84","tid":1864654,"uid":123606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:18:59.000Z","msg":"日日都諗緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0982a8879538ebe52900c13cc6fc7f7ddbb430","tid":1864654,"uid":39703,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"b638513736402be261cd88614c91a45b8c3bb28d","tid":1864654,"uid":18147,"like":35,"dislike":12,"score":23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:17:26.000Z","msg":"認受性？<br />\n<br />\n邊個出錢？<br />\n<br />\n對家有警察， 你有咩？<br />\n<br />\n國際認唔諗同你？<br />\n<br />\nConclusion, 早d 訓"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:19:09.000Z","msg":"所以先要拎返出黎講<br />\n唔通就咁坐以待斃？"},{"pid":"fefe971e60551ebec2232f52dd9ae915dc779613","tid":1864654,"uid":325079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:19:47.000Z","msg":"仲旨意呢個政府等含扌然...."},{"pid":"3b674b3aa75e2bd923ed11ce7c6d6c1a92c8a229","tid":1864654,"uid":39703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202